# --- Rust ---
# Build output — huge, fully regenerable from source. Never commit.
/target

# Backup files left by older rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# NOTE: Cargo.lock is intentionally NOT ignored.
# Mythos is a binary, so committing Cargo.lock pins exact dependency
# versions for reproducible builds. (Only libraries omit it.)

# --- IDE (JetBrains: RustRover / CLion) ---
.idea/

# --- Engine testing / self-play output ---
# fastchess / cutechess match logs and game records
*.pgn
*.log
sprt_*.txt

# --- NNUE networks (when you get there) ---
# Trained nets are large binaries. Ignore them here; if you want them
# versioned, use git-lfs rather than committing them directly.
*.nnue

# --- OS junk ---
.DS_Store

# --- Claude Code ---
CLAUDE.md

# --- Ginormous Opening Books ---
xtask/books/*.epd